'''{{class|Actor}}'''
__NOTOC__clearscope bool '''CanTalk''' () const {{git|92dbdd3}}
== Usage == Returns if the calling actor can talk to the player (Has an attached [[ZDoom_Strife_Dialog_Format|conversation script]], isn't dead, and not {{flag|INCOMBAT| in combat}}).
== See also == *[[HasConversation]] - ONLY check if the actor has a conversation script.
